These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-4-1::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, collecting, gardening, hiking, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 6 different favourite colors: white, turquise, aquamarine, fuchsia, blue, ebony
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, goat, lizard, pony
The people have 6 different jobs:  musician, security-guard, project-manager, manager, designer, fisherman
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
 4. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the owner of the pony is the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the manager is between the musician and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 9. the manager is the person who likes white##1
10. the musician is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
13. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
14. the designer is in an odd position##4
15. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
16. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who likes turquise##1
17. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
18. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
19. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
20. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
21. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |   5   |      6       |
| Hobby         | collecting | gardening  | skydiving | hiking     | chess | magic-tricks |
| Color   | turquise  | aquamarine   | fuchsia | white   | ebony  | blue       |
| Pet           | lizard     | chinchilla | cat       | goat       | frog  | pony         |
| Job     | designer | security-guard     | musician       | manager | project-manager  | fisherman          |

