House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, colonial, craftsman, palace, victorian
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, handball, golf, cycling, rugby, skateboarding
 1. the person watching action movies is the palace house##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person eating grapes is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the palace house is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 8. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
11. the palace house is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
12. the person eating banana is on the right of the palace house##1
13. the palace house is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
14. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
15. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
16. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
17. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating banana##1
18. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
19. the person eating apricot is the person watching musical movies##1
20. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
21. the person eating cherry is between the victorian house and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |     5      |    6     |
