 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
12. the dunhill-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
14. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1
15. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
16. the baccarat-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the fan of jazz##2
17. the davidoff-smoker is the fan of folk##1
18. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to new-york and the person who's hobby is writing##2
19. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

